flowchart LR
    C[Customer] -->|Dials USSD / Uses Hubtel App or Web Mall| HPS[Hubtel Programmable Services]
    HPS -->|Push request: Initiation/Response| SI[Service Interaction Endpoint]

    subgraph APP[Restaurant Backend]
        SI --> OC[Order Controller]
        OC --> OS[OrderService]
        OS --> DB[(Database)]
        OS --> LS[LoyaltyService]
        OS --> DS[DeliveryService]
        OS --> SMS[NotificationService]
        LS --> DB
        DS --> DB
        SMS --> DB
        AUD[AuditLogService] --> DB
    end

    OS -->|All status transitions| AUD
    DS -->|Sensitive verification events| AUD

    SI -->|AddToCart response| HPS
    HPS -->|Service Fulfillment callback after payment| CB[Payment Callback Endpoint]
    CB -->|Verify signature + validate payload| OS
    CB --> AUD

    OS -->|Optional: if no final callback after 5 min| TSC[Hubtel Transaction Status Check API]
    TSC --> OS

    OS -->|Service fulfillment callback within 1 hour| HCB[Hubtel Fulfillment Callback Endpoint]

    SMS -->|Send SMS| HSMS[Hubtel SMS API]
    HSMS --> SMS

    subgraph ADMIN[Admin Dashboard]
        UI[Admin UI]
        AUTH[Auth Layer JWT HttpOnly + CSRF]
    end
    UI --> AUTH --> OC
    AUTH --> AUD

    DB --> AN[Analytics SQL Queries]
    AN --> UI
